---
import ContentPage from '../layouts/ContentPage.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: `${SITE.url}/` },
  { name: 'Terms of Use', url: `${SITE.url}/terms/` },
];
---
<ContentPage
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="The terms governing your use of Pool Shock Calculator, including our disclaimer of warranties and limitation of liability."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <p><em>Last updated: {SITE.dataUpdated}.</em></p>

  <p>
    By using Pool Shock Calculator ({SITE.url}), you agree to these terms. If you do
    not agree, please do not use the site.
  </p>

  <h2>Informational use only</h2>
  <p>
    The calculators and content on this site are provided for general informational
    and educational purposes. They produce <strong>estimates</strong> based on the
    values you enter and published reference data. They are not professional,
    chemical safety, or medical advice, and are not a substitute for the directions
    printed on your chemical products.
  </p>

  <h2>Follow product labels and handle chemicals safely</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Always read and follow the dosing and safety instructions on your product’s label; the label overrides any figure from this site.</li>
    <li>Never mix pool chemicals with each other, and always add chemicals to water, never water to chemicals.</li>
    <li>Store chemicals safely, away from children, and use appropriate protective equipment.</li>
    <li>Re-test your water and wait until free chlorine returns to a safe level before swimming.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>No warranties</h2>
  <p>
    The site is provided “as is” and “as available” without warranties of any kind,
    express or implied, including accuracy, fitness for a particular purpose, or
    non-infringement. Water chemistry varies with many factors we can’t measure, so
    we do not warrant that any result will be correct for your specific pool.
  </p>

  <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the fullest extent permitted by law, {SITE.publisher} and its contributors
    are not liable for any damages arising from your use of this site or reliance on
    its results, including damage to pools, equipment, property, or health. You use
    the site and any calculated dose at your own risk.
  </p>

  <h2>External and affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    We may link to third-party sites and products, including affiliate links. We are
    not responsible for the content, products, or policies of those third parties.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
  <p>
    We may revise these terms as the site changes. Continued use after an update
    means you accept the revised terms.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about these terms? Email <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>.
  </p>
</ContentPage>
